spec_data.Name: perl-Devel-Caller-IgnoreNamespaces
spec_data.Description:
If your module should be ignored by caller(), just like Hook::LexWrap is
by its magic caller(), then call this module's register() subroutine
with its name.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 10:53:15 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Make available a function which can ignore name-spaces that you tell it about
